  <thing id="fMPNMPInfl" name="Influential" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: Choose one specific sphere for the hero to hold influence over. To affect that sphere of influence, the hero must make a level check, adding his or her Charisma modifier. The DC to affect that sphere of influence is below.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: If the hero is connected in the sphere of influence, he or she receives a +1 circumstance bonus to the roll. If the hero has an ally in the sphere of influence, he or she receives a +3 circumstance bonus to the roll.\n\nDC             Effect\n15              Minor Favor - Learn about recent gossip in the field.\n20              Serious Favor - Perform minor tasks within the field.\n25              Major Favor - Perform major tasks within the field.\n30              Ridiculous Favor - Alter the landscape of the field." compset="Feat" summary="You have influence within a specific sphere.">
