  <thing id="trMPNMPCul" name="Cult Member" description="A Cult Member includes heretics, followers of fringe religions, &quot;family&quot; members, alternative lifestyles, and sect members.\n\nChoose one of the following skills: Bluff, Intimidate, Knowledge (Arcana), Knowledge (Religion), Linguistics, Sense Motive, Spellcraft\n\nYou gain a +1 trait bonus on this skill and it is always considered a class skill for you.\n\nWealth Bonus: +2" compset="Trait" summary="A Cult Member includes heretics, followers of fringe religions" uniqueness="useronce">
