  <thing id="cMPNMPAcFr" name="Arcane Firearm" description="The gunmage crafts a special firearm that can be used to cast spells. As a move action, the gunmage can &quot;load&quot; a touch spell he has memorized with a casting time of no more than one action into his firearm. As a standard action, the gunmage can fire the weapon. The gunmage rolls to hit as normal and if successful, gains the benefit of the gun&apos;s mundane ammunition and the loaded spell effect. \n\nAlternately, the gunmage can spend a Hero Point and &quot;load&quot; a ranged spell he has memorized with a casting time of no more than one action into his firearm as a move action. No ammunition may be used when a ranged spell is loaded into the firearm. When using this ability, the gunmage&apos;s Ammunition training does not apply to the missiles fired from the firearm.\n\nOnly one spell of any type can be loaded into an arcane firearm at one time. &quot;Loading&quot; a spell into an arcane firearm with provoke an attack of opportunity. If the gunmage is struck for any damage while &quot;loading&quot; an arcane firearm, he must make a Concentration check to avoid losing the spell." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You can craft a weapon that fires spells." uniqueness="unique">
