  <thing id="cMPNMPProf" name="Profile" description="By making a Perception check (DC 10) when talking to witnesses, the vigilante compiles a physical description, including distinguishing markings and visible mannerisms. The vigilante can expand the profile by making a Perception check (DC 15) involving the scene or other evidence linked to the suspect. If successful, the vigilante combines eyewitness accounts with forensic evidence to develop a profile of the suspect&apos;s method of operation. This provides a +2 circumstance bonus on any skill checks made to uncover additional evidence or otherwise locate and capture the suspect." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You can take the observations of a single person and construct a personality profile from it." uniqueness="unique">
